// A dot-prefixed identifier without a trailing ':' is mistakenly treated as
// an instruction mnemonic by the parser, since dot-prefix is part of the
// identifier and the strict label parser requires the ':'. The encoder
// surfaces this as an UnknownMnemonic, and the diagnostic enrichment in
// `build_encode_diagnostic` recognises the dot prefix and tells the user
// they likely forgot the colon.

func main {
    nop
.exit
    nop
}
